'''''Ceol 2010''''' was the 2010 [[Seachtain na Gaeilge]] (Irish Language Week) music album released during ''Seachtain na Gaeilge'' in March 2010. The album features songs in [[Irish language|Irish]] by [[The Coronas]], [[Bell X1 (band)|Bell X1]], [[Gemma Hayes]], [[Luan Parle]], [[Mundy]], [[The Saw Doctors]], [[Kíla]], [[Eddi Reader]] and [[The Swell Season]]. The album reached #3 in the Irish Compilation Album charts. All proceeds from sales of the CD went to the children's charity [[Barnardo's]].

