*Urbano Sacchetti (1864&ndash;1912)
*Clemente Sacchetti (1912&ndash;1919)
*Luigi Tommaso Sacchetti (1919&ndash;1936)
*Enrico Urbano Sacchetti (1936&ndash;1958)
*Urbano Sacchetti (1958&ndash;1970)

